Project Overview


This project is a simple, clean static website for a restaurant, created as part of a group assignment to demonstrate how AWS services can be used to host and manage a website.



The website was built using standard web technologies and deployed on Amazon S3 as a static website.

We also created a presentation explaining the AWS benefits, concepts, and services used.

ğŸ¯ 
Project Objectives
Build a functional static restaurant website

Host the website using Amazon S3 Static Website Hosting

Store website images in an S3 bucket

Understand cloud hosting fundamentals

Create presentation slides covering AWS benefits and how the website uses cloud services

Practice teamwork, documentation, and cloud deployment skills

