AWS Services in This Project


ğŸ”¹ 
Amazon S3 (Static Website Hosting)


We created an S3 bucket and enabled static website hosting.

The bucket stores:

Website HTML files

CSS and JavaScript files

Images (menu photos, restaurant logo, interior photos)



S3 provides:

High availability

Easy hosting

Pay-as-you-go pricing

No server configuration



ğŸ”¹ 
IAM


IAM was used to:

Manage permissions

Ensure the bucket is accessible for web hosting

Control who can upload or modify files

