Website Features
Clean and simple restaurant homepage

Menu section

Restaurant images stored in the S3 bucket

Contact details section

Responsive layout (optional depending on your version)

ğŸš€ 
Deployment Steps (Summary)
Built HTML, CSS, and JS files as a team

Created an Amazon S3 bucket

Uploaded the website files into the bucket

Enabled Static Website Hosting

Updated bucket policy to allow public access (only for static hosting)

Copied the S3 website URL to access the website online

Uploaded images into the bucket so the website loads everything correctly

